column2: Select distinct ?cf ?cf_value ?time WHERE {  ?cf ecfo:hasApplicablePeriod/time:hasEnd/time:inXSDDate ?time; rdf:value ?cf_value. Filter (?time < now())}
Select distinct ?cf ?cf_value  WHERE {  ?cf a ecfo:EmissionConversionFactor; rdf:value ?cf_value. FILTER NOT EXISTS {?cf prov:wasDerivedFrom ?source.}}
Select distinct ?cf ?cf_value  WHERE {  ?cf a ecfo:EmissionConversionFactor; rdf:value ?cf_value. FILTER NOT EXISTS {?cf ecfo:hasApplicablePeriod/time:hasBeginning ?start.}}
Select distinct ?cf ?cf_value  WHERE { ?cf a ecfo:EmissionConversionFactor; rdf:value ?cf_value. FILTER NOT EXISTS {?cf ecfo:hasApplicablePeriod/time:hasEnd ?end.}}
